<h2>Smt. Parvatibai Chowgule College of Arts and Science</h2>
<p>Smt. Parvatibai Chowgule College or fondly known as Chowgule College is the oldest institution in Goa providing higher education since 1961. Over this span our campus has undergone many changes and our aim has always been to stay synced with modern technologies and methodologies to provide best infrastructure and learning environment to our students. As a token of our endeavour to augment the learning standards our campus, NAAC awarded us with A grade in 2008 and we are striving harder to maintain our standards. 
We offer graduate and post-graduate course in faculties of Arts and Science. Our labs and entire campus is equipped with state of the art infrastructure to cater to the demands of our learning and teaching community. For more details about the college, please visit http://www.chowgules.ac.in/
Department of Computer Science</p>
<p>The Department of Computer Science was established in 1986 and hence it became the first department in entire Goa to provide IT oriented courses. We began by offering Post Graduate Diploma course in Computer Applications to cater to the emerging needs of IT industry, later started B. Sc Computer Science & B.Sc Computer Applications (Vocational). Now we offer a post-graduate program ie M.Sc-IT and PGCET along with previously initiated course.
We have state of the art labs and other IT infrastructure and are always in forefront in upgrading to provide the best technical environment for our student. We also have highly qualified faculties who have a strong research as well as industry background.</p>
<p>Apart from regular classes, we also conduct various orientation courses, seminars, guest lectures from industry experts, conferences etc. which helps our student to interact with industry and get to know about its current needs. Our ex-students are well placed in companies like TCS, Infosys, Persisten Systems, Andrew Telecom, Sapna Tech etc. while some are pursuing their higher studies and research in universities in India and abroad. For more details visit www.chowgules.ac.in</p>

